[ ] move felix config template writing from config to start

m2ee-tools 0.5.1
[ ] moar leveraging the version comparison for cli command availability signaling
[ ] add command to display cache_statistics
[ ] munin: show cache statistics (amount of transient objects in cache)
[ ] implement munin/nagios plugins by importing m2ee instead of abusing the CLI tool

backlog
